Tom Daley hopes his new 'firework' dive can help him win Olympic gold at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Games . 
  The 20-year-old has spent the winter modifying the dive with his new coach Jane Figueiredo . 
  Daley won bronze at the British Championships . 
  He says he is enjoying diving more than ever after relocating from Plymouth to London . 
  He will compete at the FINA World Series in London next month . 
 